title: East Side King
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Kitchen at the back of the top floor of The Four Horsemen bar with indoor picnic table seating. Order at the window, take a number and staff brings food to you. Fried brussels sprouts come in a salad. Vegan and gluten free items are marked and comprise a large percentage of the menu.
